And my voice and my throat is
so sore, like that night I

00:22:37.575 --> 00:22:40.655
couldn't swallow my own spit.

00:22:40.655 --> 00:22:45.200
Now I know why men for eons
have been such dicks.

00:22:45.200 --> 00:22:50.040
Because if you have a really
miserable, hard physical day,

00:22:50.040 --> 00:22:51.140
I couldn't talk.

00:22:51.140 --> 00:22:52.460
I couldn't smile.

00:22:52.460 --> 00:22:56.910
I was just an unhappy zombie,
which is how I imagine men

00:22:56.910 --> 00:22:59.630
come home from like mining as.

00:23:02.200 --> 00:23:04.690
My wife was like, you can't--

00:23:04.690 --> 00:23:05.455
this was the day before
I was supposed

00:23:05.455 --> 00:23:06.450
to fight Randy Couture.

00:23:06.450 --> 00:23:08.330
And she's like, you can't
do that tomorrow.

00:23:08.330 --> 00:23:10.430
Part of being a man is
knowing when to quit.

00:23:13.050 --> 00:23:15.030
I was in enough of a daze where
I was like, yeah, that

00:23:15.030 --> 00:23:15.520
