00:23:15.520 --> 00:23:17.940
Like anything you say right
now would make sense, like

00:23:17.940 --> 00:23:20.450
being a man is knowing how
to arrange flowers.

00:23:20.450 --> 00:23:21.990
Anything would've made sense.

00:23:21.990 --> 00:23:24.660
And so I woke up the next
morning and this

00:23:24.660 --> 00:23:25.700
fog had kind of lifted.

00:23:25.700 --> 00:23:28.390
My throat still killed, but
I was able to function.

00:23:28.390 --> 00:23:31.320
So I went and I fought
Randy Couture.

00:23:31.320 --> 00:23:35.360
