00:23:36.780 --> 00:23:39.760
But he would not talk to me.

00:23:39.760 --> 00:23:41.300
He just like pointed.

00:23:41.300 --> 00:23:42.440
And we went to this ring.

00:23:42.440 --> 00:23:45.270
I was so, so scared.

00:23:45.270 --> 00:23:48.410
But I was hoping it would
be over in five seconds.

00:23:48.410 --> 00:23:50.730
He would either hit me
and I would blackout.

00:23:50.730 --> 00:23:53.990
Or he would get me into some
