00:25:32.900 --> 00:25:35.300
But in the end, I decided
not to give it to him.

00:25:35.300 --> 00:25:39.330
Because the only way
a man learns is by

00:25:39.330 --> 00:25:41.430
doing, not by reading.

00:25:41.430 --> 00:25:44.760
So I don't think he'll
ever see that list.

00:25:44.760 --> 00:25:48.700
But I'll put it up online,
